name: FNF - Test Engine [Kapi, Matt, sarvente...]
description:
A friday night funkin test engine made by me.

Note: None of the sprites in-game are mine.

-Controls:

 +W, A, S and D.

 +BackSpace (for the command menu)

 +Enter (to close the command menu/confirm the command)

-Characters:

 +click BackSpace and type in:

  •    /load tank (for tankman)
  •    /load sarv (for sarvente)
  •    /load tricky (for tricky)
  •    /load kapi (for kapi)
  •    /load zardy (for zardy)
  •    /load matt (for le funny wii matt)

-Character list:

  •  tankman
  •  sarvente
  •  tricky
  •  kapi
  •  zardy
  •  matt

Feel free to make gameplays or whatever of this, just don't reupload the engine.
